title: Summonses rift colour change?
body: I don't know if it's just me but does anyone feel like the colour of the normal summonses rift map has changed slightly? It kinda feels off but I accept it

replies.body: I was thinking the same thing, though it might just be coming back from the Winter Rift that it seems different.
Yeah true i did not think about that. Oh well my eyes have adjusted to it now
Do you realise that normal games are running on the Winter version right?
I mean when I play ranked it seems like it has a higher contrast. Must just be my eyes but yeah I'm not a dumbass haha
